  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main focus of the project is to determine to what degree myocardial energy metabolism is
      linked to impaired function in human cardiomyocytes, whether exercise training and remote
      ischemic preconditioning can restore cardiomyocyte function and whether this is linked to
      improved mitochondrial and cell function.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
